reviewText: It has good footage, but it's definitely akin to the weird, 90s/2000s-fabulous MLS uniforms. There's also lots of nostalgia for the "good old days" of the MLS shootout, Floridian MLS teams, and Landon Donovan's bleached hair. All I'm saying is this: the MLS has come a long way since this DVD was made, and in my opinion the league deserves better.
